<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>AP scores are accepted by Barstow College for college credit in certain classes. A student scoring a 3, 4, or 5 on College Board Advanced Placement Exams should contact a counselor for more information.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.barstow.edu/Academics/catalog.pdf" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
